## Build infrastructure

### `Justfile`

```just
# Compile all plugin binaries for the host platform
build-plugins:
    docker compose run --rm \
      -e GOOS={{goos}} -e GOARCH={{goarch}} -e BIN_EXT={{bin_ext}} \
      -e VERSION={{version}} -e COMMIT={{commit}} -e DATE={{date}} \
      build-plugins

# build now also compiles plugins
build: build-plugins
    docker compose run --rm \
      -e GOOS={{goos}} -e GOARCH={{goarch}} -e BIN_EXT={{bin_ext}} \
      -e VERSION={{version}} -e COMMIT={{commit}} -e DATE={{date}} \
      build
```

### `compose.yml`

- `build-plugins` service: iterates `plugins/getter/*` and `plugins/setter/*`,
  compiles each to `bin/status-getter-<name>` / `bin/status-setter-<name>`.
- `chrome` service: `chromedp/headless-shell:latest`, used by integration tests.
- `test-integration-tripit` service: runs plugin integration tests with Chrome
  and sandbox credentials.

