## Unit Test Scenarios (`trips_test.go`, table-driven)

| Scenario | Expected |
|----------|----------|
| No trips in response | `[]Event{}` |
| Trip with two flight segments (AA356 + AA2360) | StartsAt = depart+ingress; EndsAt = last arrive; flights len=2 |
| Trip without flights | StartsAt/EndsAt from start/end_date; flights=[] |
| now before starts_on | not returned |
| now after ends_on | not returned |
| TRIP_ENDED note present | ended=true in Meta |
| Single-segment flight (single object, not array) | normalised; flights len=1 |
| TripIt returns Trip as single object not array | normalised, no panic |
| API returns non-200 | error returned |
| Missing primary_location | city = "Anywhere, Earth" |
| `TRIPIT_INGRESS_TIME_MINUTES=90` env var | StartsAt = depart + 5400s |
| `ingress_minutes` param set | overrides env var |
